<div class="title">Night Like No Other (Monsters)</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria, Mushrooms - P. cubensis & Calea zacatechichi</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=norman&Exact=1">norman</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; norman. "Night Like No Other (Monsters): An Experience with Amanita muscaria, Mushrooms - P. cubensis & Calea zacatechichi (exp23345)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 20, 2003. erowid.org/exp/23345</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
